query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('access-vba',
'android-listview',
'frontend',
'github',
'logging',
'python-3.6',
'r',
'solr',
'sql-update',
'subquery',
'time-series',
'tomcat')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Citizen Patrol',
'Commentator',
'Constituent',
'Curious',
'Famous Question',
'Guru',
'Nice Answer',
'Nice Question',
'Self-Learner',
'Student',
'Tenacious') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
